data.description: Very unique property in Salem (not city).  Rural area of Salem with good commuting access.  This is a mixed use home.  Residential and Office/Professional use. This also can be converted back to a single family.  Possible 5 bedroom home with 2 full baths.   Ideally this would be fantastic for a professional to live in the residential side, 2 large bedrooms, 1 full bath, large living room with fire place, dining room and large kitchen.  The residential side has been completely updated, new kitchen, bath, flooring, appliances etc. Have to see it to appreciate the workmanship.  The office side is equipped with 5 private offices, reception area, waiting room, 1/2 bath and storage area.  Great for a real estate office, dentist, chiropractor, family Doc, tattoo shop etc.  This home could be easily converted back to 100% residential and can be a 5 or 6 bedroom house with 2-3 full bathrooms.  Come take a look,  great opportunity for a large family or a professional.
